.TH update_device.conf "1" "@MONTH@ @YEAR@" "mhvtl @VERSION@" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
update_device.conf \- Utility to update device.conf to version 4
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B update_device.conf
.SH DESCRIPTION
.\" Add any additional description here
.PP
This script updates the device.conf file to version 4, and sets
the library index to one more than the number of drives found.
